<%# Per-calculator disclaimer — AdSense compliance for financial/health content %>
<div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 dark:border-gray-700/60">
  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-white leading-relaxed">
    <strong class="text-gray-500 dark:text-white">Disclaimer:</strong>
    This calculator is for informational and educational purposes only. Results are estimates and should not be considered professional
    <% if local_assigns[:category] == "finance" %>
      financial, tax, or investment
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "health" %>
      medical or health
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "construction" %>
      engineering or construction
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "education" %>
      academic, financial aid, or educational planning
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "pets" %>
      veterinary or animal nutrition
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "automotive" %>
      automotive, mechanical, or safety
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "cooking" %>
      food safety, nutrition, or culinary
    <% elsif local_assigns[:category] == "photography" %>
      professional photography or optical
    <% else %>
      expert
    <% end %>
    advice. Consult a qualified professional before making decisions based on these calculations. See our full <%= link_to "Disclaimer", disclaimer_path, class: "text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 underline" %>.
  </p>
</div>
